  "body": "The [EIP-2929](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-2929) is missing test coverage for OOG case in the newly added cold access checks in state access instructions. I can observer these at least for `EXTCODESIZE`, `EXTCODECOPY` and `EXTCODEHASH`. But also `SLOAD` may be affected (because of the different implementation this is not visible in the code coverage report).\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/573380/114553178-a6437200-9c65-11eb-8aa8-5dd8431fa7ab.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/573380/114553262-bf4c2300-9c65-11eb-86ed-419f94d7e6c8.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/573380/114553343-d2f78980-9c65-11eb-848e-dc2f141b2e2f.png)\r\n",
